# Project Overview

This project is a browser extension built using WXT (Web Extension Tools) and React.

## Key Directories
- [entrypoints/](mdc:entrypoints/) - Contains all extension entry points (background scripts, content scripts, popup)
- [components/](mdc:components/) - Reusable React components
- [lib/](mdc:lib/) - Utility functions, hooks, and helper code
- [assets/](mdc:assets/) - Static assets like images
- [public/](mdc:public/) - Public assets that are copied as-is to the extension

## Configuration Files
- [wxt.config.ts](mdc:wxt.config.ts) - WXT configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [components.json](mdc:components.json) - Component configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts

## Build & Development
Run development server: `npm run dev`
Build the extension: `npm run build`
Build for Firefox: `npm run build:firefox`
